  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/imagecapturecore\/icreturnconnectionerror\/ejectfailed\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T21:34:49Z\n---\n\n# ejectFailed\n\n**Type Property**\n\nDevice reports eject has failed.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic var ejectFailed: ICReturnConnectionError.Code { get }\n```\n\n## Error Codes\n\n- **closedSessionSuddenly**: Device closed session without request.\n- **driverExited**: Device driver exited without request.\n- **ejectedSuddenly**: Device ejected without request.\n- **failedToOpen**: Failed to open a connection to the device.\n- **failedToOpenDevice**: Failed to open the device.\n- **sessionAlreadyOpen**: Device reports session is already open.\n- **ICReturnConnectionError.Code**\n\n",
